    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Slip-on shoes with low-cut, rounded or V-shaped throat, and usually a medium to high heel; sometimes made with open toe or open heel in sling-back style.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
